latestIgtvVideos.title: We are Freelancers-We are beyond limitless!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Dear Freelancer ,you know due to Covid 19,Freelancers such as WE have been hit hard financially and many among us don’t have enough savings.Some budding ones have no saving for even a couple of months and they are sinking towards negativity or worse to depression.You May not now me,I may not know you.
But we connect on one grounds and that is FREELANCERS. 
As a freelancer , we took a initiative to bring together a set of freelancers from all across India for a short film called ‘FREELANCERS-Beyond Limitless’  to MOTIVATE and bring back CONFIDENCE in each FREELANCERS. And remind them that they are passionate and they dared to dream and success and will be unstoppable under and over Covid19. #freelancers #beyondlimitless

latestIgtvVideos.title: Mermaid Hair Tutorial 🧜‍♀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Ladiesssss ❤️ Filmed this look on a request , get that nice and beautiful wavy hair in no time , without any heat used 🙂
Hope you will like it . ❤️ Some tips : 
1. Bfore braiding your hair apply a good hair protein cream/ serum. 
2. Braid your hair in 4-5 parts based on how you want it to be . (Small/big waves)
3 . If your hair is Smooth and silky like mine , do a tighter 4 braids . 
4 . Avoid doing it on wet hair . 
5 . Leave the braids just like that overnight , and open them in the morning . 
6. Add some serum for that quick shine and volume . 
Thanks for watching ❤️ .
.
